{"tid":1754790,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"本地酒樓集團首灃控股中期虧損擴大49%","createTime":"2019-11-25T10:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T10:28:43.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b424228e6bbfe0bc1547379fb57de0197df9b582","tid":1754790,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"本地酒樓集團首灃控股公布，截至9月底止，中期虧損4247萬港元，虧損按年急增49%，不派中期股息。<br />\n<br />\n期內，收入3.32億元，按年減少0.3%；毛利率增加1.2個百分點至75.7%。<br />\n<br />\n公司指，面對過去數月的艱困業務狀況及環境，收入按年下跌為4年來首見，管理層會密切監察經濟及業務環境發展。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494397-20191125.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494397-20191125.htm&d=S%2FsiG%2FBE2bBILTWTz3VeJiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=6231f9a0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1494397-20191125.htm&h=ecde858c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1494397-20191125.htm</a>"}]}